---
// DonateSection - Support section with payment placeholders
---

<section class="section donate-section" id="donate">
	<div class="container-narrow">
		<div class="donate-content">
			<h2>Support This Project</h2>
			<p class="donate-intro">
				If spec-driven development has helped you build better software, consider supporting this free resource. Your contribution helps maintain and improve the agents.
			</p>

			<div class="payment-options">
				<div class="payment-card">
					<div class="payment-icon">ðŸ’³</div>
					<h3>Card Payment</h3>
					<p>Support via credit or debit card</p>
					<div class="coming-soon">
						<span>Coming Soon</span>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="payment-card">
					<div class="payment-icon">â‚¿</div>
					<h3>Crypto Payment</h3>
					<p>Support with cryptocurrency</p>
					<div class="coming-soon">
						<span>Coming Soon</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<p class="donate-note">
				Payment integrations are in development. For now, the spec-architect agent remains <strong>completely free</strong> with no restrictions.
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.donate-section {
		background: var(--color-pastel-purple);
		text-align: center;
	}

	.donate-content {
		max-width: 700px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.donate-intro {
		font-size: var(--text-xl);
		margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
		color: var(--color-text-secondary);
	}

	.payment-options {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
		gap: var(--space-6);
		margin: var(--space-12) 0;
	}

	.payment-card {
		background: var(--color-white);
		padding: var(--space-8);
		border-radius: var(--border-radius);
		border: var(--border-width) solid var(--color-border);
		position: relative;
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-brutal-sm);
	}

	.payment-icon {
		font-size: 3rem;
		margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
	}

	.payment-card h3 {
		font-size: var(--text-2xl);
		margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
		color: var(--color-text-primary);
	}

	.payment-card p {
		font-size: var(--text-base);
		margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
		color: var(--color-text-secondary);
	}

	.coming-soon {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		padding: var(--space-2) var(--space-4);
		background: var(--color-pastel-yellow);
		color: var(--color-gray-900);
		border-radius: var(--border-radius);
		font-size: var(--text-sm);
		font-weight: 700;
		border: 2px solid var(--color-border);
	}

	.donate-note {
		font-size: var(--text-base);
		color: var(--color-text-secondary);
		margin-top: var(--space-8);
		padding: var(--space-4);
		background: var(--color-white);
		border-radius: var(--border-radius);
		margin-bottom: 0;
		border: var(--border-width) solid var(--color-border);
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-brutal-sm);
	}

	.donate-note strong {
		color: var(--color-primary);
	}
</style>
